                            <comment id="13294725" author="kevinwilfong" created="Wed, 13 Jun 2012 23:38:24 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached a diff for this issue here &lt;a href=&quot;https://reviews.facebook.net/D3633&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://reviews.facebook.net/D3633&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
